      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">The Treasury, ¶ Melbourne,13th October, 1894. ¶ (COPY) ¶ No. 7744 ¶ Sir,...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">94.10.16d</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Charles Topp</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">No.3883, unit 105B,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>pp. 1-2,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>VPRS 1187/P, outward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Copies of Eaton's letter to Topp were sent by the latter to the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>heads of the various<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>sub-departments within the Chief Secretary's Department.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>The covering note is undated but the index of outward correspondence gives the date as 16 October.</p>
               </note>The Treasury,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne,13th October, 1894.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">(COPY)</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">No. 7744</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I am directed to request that the Treasurer may be furnished with the following information as to the Department of the Honorable the Chief Secretary.</p>
            <table n="">
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.075in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.075in; ">
                     <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.075in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.075in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">1. Number of Employees on the 1st January 1893 —</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.075in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.075in; ">
                     <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.075in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.075in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">Permanent</p>
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">Temporary</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.075in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.075in; ">
                     <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.075in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.075in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">2. Number of Employees on the 30th June 1894,</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.075in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.075in; ">
                     <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.075in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.075in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; margin-left: 0.3333in; "
                        xml:lang="en">(a) <space unit="chars" quantity="4"/>Permanent</p>
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; margin-left: 0.3333in; "
                        xml:lang="en">(b) <space unit="chars" quantity="3"/>Temporary</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.075in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.075in; ">
                     <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.075in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.075in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">3. Particulars of any appointments made during that period —</p>
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>1st January 1893 – 30th June 1894 – from outside the Service</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
               <row>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.075in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.075in; ">
                     <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
                  </cell>
                  <cell style="border: none; padding-top: 0in; padding-left: 0.075in; padding-bottom: 0in; padding-right: 0.075in; ">
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Permanent</p>
                     <p rend="letter"
                        style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Temporary</p>
                  </cell>
               </row>
            </table>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Mr Turner would be glad to have this information as early as practicable</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have &amp;c</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>H. F. Eaton</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Under Treasurer</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Under Secretary</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Forwarded for the immediate attention of the [...]<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Space left empty for title of<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>sub-department<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>head to be entered.<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>The covering note is unsigned but the document would have been sent by<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Topp as<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Under Secretary.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>so far as it relates to his Branch of the Department.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
         </div>
      </body>
   </text>
